text: Dichostates flavopictus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Quedenfeldt in 1882.BioLib.cz - Dichostates flavopictus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It contains the varietas Dichostates flavopictus var. bimaculatus. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1882
title: Dichostates flavopictus
